import { Row, Container, CounterValue, Content } from "./styles"
import CardPedido from "../../Components/CardPedido"
import Header from "../../Components/Header"
import { useState } from "react"

function Marmita() {
    const [teste, setTeste] = useState(2)


    return (<>
        <Header title='teste'/>

        <Container>
            <Content>
                
                <CardPedido title="aqui esta um pedido " value={teste}  >
                               
                </CardPedido>

            </Content>
        </Container>
    
    
    </>)
}


export {Marmita}
